<!DOCTYPE ui:UiBinder SYSTEM "http://dl.google.com/gwt/DTD/xhtml.ent">
<ui:UiBinder xmlns:ui="urn:ui:com.google.gwt.uibinder" xmlns:g="urn:import:com.google.gwt.user.client.ui">
    <ui:style>
        .box {
            margin: 5px;
        }
        .code {
            font-family: monospace; 
        }
    </ui:style>
    <g:DockLayoutPanel unit="EM">
        <g:west size="12">
            <g:VerticalPanel addStyleNames="{style.box}">
                <g:Hyperlink ui:field="jsonToPojo" targetHistoryToken="fromJsonAsPojo">JSON &rarr; POJO</g:Hyperlink>
                <g:Hyperlink ui:field="jsonToGxtModel" targetHistoryToken="fromJsonAsGxtModel">JSON &rarr; GXT Model</g:Hyperlink>
                <g:Hyperlink ui:field="xmlToPojo" targetHistoryToken="fromXmlAsPojo">XML &rarr; POJO</g:Hyperlink>
                <g:Hyperlink ui:field="xmlToGxtModel" targetHistoryToken="fromXmlAsGxtModel">XML &rarr; GXT Model</g:Hyperlink>
            </g:VerticalPanel>
        </g:west>
        <g:north size="13">
            <g:HTML addStyleNames="{style.box}">
                This demo demonstrates the features of <a href="http://code.google.com/p/piriti/" target="_blank">Piriti.</a><br />
                Therefore the demo provides a 'books' resources which returns three books. 
                The resource is available in two representations:
                <ul>
                    <li><a href="/rest/v1/books" target="_blank">XML</a></li>
                    <li>JSON. To see the representation use some kind of rest client (e.g. <a href="http://hypertopic.org/index.php/RESTClient" target="_blank">RESTClient for Firefox</a>), 
                    call '/rest/v1/books' and set the 'Accept' header to 'application/json'</li>
                </ul>
                Using the four links you can call the resource and convert the data to a book POJO or a book GXT model. 
                For each request the relevant source code and time in milliseconds is displayed. The time is only the 
                processing time (network traffic is not included). 
            </g:HTML>
        </g:north>
        <g:center>
            <g:ScrollPanel addStyleNames="{style.box}">
                <g:Label ui:field="sourceCode" addStyleNames="{style.code}" />
            </g:ScrollPanel>
        </g:center>
        <g:south size="2">
            <g:Label ui:field="status" addStyleNames="{style.box}" />
        </g:south>
    </g:DockLayoutPanel>
</ui:UiBinder> 